text: "Stranger in a Strange Land" is a 1986 song by English heavy metal band Iron Maiden and taken from their sixth studio album Somewhere in Time. It went to number 18 in Ireland and number 22 in the United Kingdom. == Track listing == '7" single ;12" single Category:1986 songs Category:Iron Maiden songs Category:Heavy metal
